# Security rules (critical)
- NEVER store plaintext passwords or vault keys to disk
- Do not change AES-256-GCM format without a migration
- Do not log decrypted field values
- Do not bypass get_vault_key() dependency
- Call secure_wipe() when evicting keys — never skip it
- No test suite — be conservative with crypto/auth changes

# Key files
| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| backend/main.py | FastAPI app, CORS, rate limiter, lifespan |
| backend/crypto.py | encrypt(), decrypt(), derive_key(), secure_wipe() |
| backend/vault_store.py | VaultKeyStore singleton, thread-safe |
| backend/dependencies.py | get_current_user(), get_jti(), get_vault_key() |
| backend/models.py | SQLAlchemy 2.x Mapped[] models |
| backend/schemas.py | Pydantic *Create/*Update/*Out schemas |
| backend/config.py | All config from env (dotenv) |
| backend/auth/ | google_oauth.py, session.py (JWT), keychain.py |
| backend/routers/ | auth.py, entries.py, categories.py, generator.py, vault.py |
| frontend/src/api/client.ts | Axios (withCredentials: true), typed API methods |
| frontend/src/hooks/useVault.ts | TanStack Query hooks |

# Conventions
Backend:
- All config from config.py — never os.getenv() in routers
- All new routers registered in main.py via app.include_router()
- Every DB query on VaultEntry/Category must filter by user_id
- Encrypted fields: encrypt on write, decrypt in _serialize() before returning
- Rate limiting on sensitive endpoints: 5/min, 10/hr per IP

Frontend:
- All API calls through frontend/src/api/client.ts only
- TanStack Query: always invalidateQueries on mutation success
- API base via VITE_API_BASE_URL env var
- Tailwind CSS only (no CSS modules)

# Dev commands
```
./start.sh                                    # both servers
cd backend && source venv/bin/activate        # ALWAYS do this before Python
uvicorn main:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000 --reload
cd frontend && npm run dev                    # port 5173
cd frontend && npm run lint
cd frontend && npm run build
```

Backend .env lives at backend/.env (not repo root). No test suite exists.
Stack: FastAPI (Python 3.11+) + React 19/TypeScript + SQLite. macOS only (Touch ID via Keychain).